parameters.text: = You are an expert in data extraction and categorization. Analyze the attached CV data {{ $json.text }}  and extract the relevant information in JSON format using the following headers: Name Phone Email LinkedIn Skills Match Experience (Extract the full experience section) Years of Experience (Please calculate the total years of professional experience based on the provided work history in the CV. For each job listed, consider the start and end dates, or if the job is ongoing, calculate the experience as of the current date. Provide the exact number of the total years of experience across all positions listed.) Education Relevant Projects/Achievements Overall Assessment Additional Notes Department Categorization Explanation for Categorization Categorization: Categorize the CV into one of these departments: Project Manager Software Engineering Software Quality Assurance SW Architect IT Support DevOps Other Ensure the categorization is accurate and provide a concise explanation for the chosen department. If the attached file cannot be read or processed, or if any field is unavailable or unextractable, use the following JSON format: { "Name": "None", "Phone": "None", "Email": "None", "LinkedIn": "None", "Skills Match": "None", "Experience": "None", "Years of Experience": "None", "Education": "None", "Relevant Projects/Achievements": "None", "Overall Assessment": "None", "Additional Notes": "None", "Department Categorization": "Other", "Explanation for Categorization": "File could not be read or processed." } Only provide the JSON output.
